detaileddescription.para:
index_start



the starting index (included), read from right to left 




index_end



the ending index (not included), read from right to left




the representation of a slice (i.e. a subset) of the ONV (read from right to left) between index_start (included) and index_end (not included)

"010011".slice(1, 4) => "01[001]1" -> "001", where the spinor indices are: 543210 //ThisfileispartofGQCG-GQCP.
